23:30.868 --> 23:32.953
<i>That's telling me</i>
<i>that my blade</i>

23:32.953 --> 23:34.955
<i>better be</i>
<i>pretty frickin' strong</i>

23:34.955 --> 23:37.541
because it needs
to stand up to J.

23:37.541 --> 23:39.668
- Smiths, welcome
to our strength test.

23:39.668 --> 23:42.630
I'm gonna take each of
your multipurpose blades

23:42.630 --> 23:44.173
