32:24.776 --> 32:25.949
so got to do it.

32:35.120 --> 32:37.372
<i>Maybe I turned the vise</i>
<i>a little too fast</i>

32:37.372 --> 32:41.543
and it just snapped
right in half.

32:41.543 --> 32:43.795
<i>It's almost like I'm in</i>
<i>a dream or something.</i>

32:43.795 --> 32:45.964
<i>Like, it just doesn't really</i>
<i>feel like that just happened,</i>

32:45.964 --> 32:48.300
but I can't dwell on it.

32:48.300 --> 32:50.093
<i>I now have less than ten hours</i>

32:50.093 --> 32:52.262
<i>to make a totally</i>
<i>new sword blade.</i>

32:52.262 --> 32:56.224
I just sort of take a moment
of silence and collect myself

32:56.224 --> 32:58.435
<i>and then I'm off to the forge.</i>

32:58.435 --> 33:01.897
If I wasn't the underdog
