33:01.897 --> 33:05.275
<i>I learned a lot from forging</i>
<i>that first sword blade,</i>

33:05.275 --> 33:09.112
<i>but I don't know if I can get</i>
<i>this done in a day.</i>

33:09.112 --> 33:11.323
<i>♪ ♪</i>

33:11.323 --> 33:14.034
<i>- I'm working on fitting up</i>
<i>the guard, the handle,</i>

33:14.034 --> 33:17.329
