It's really just buttoning up
a lot of details.

33:20.290 --> 33:22.542
<i>My back's sore.</i>
<i>My shoulders are sore.</i>

33:22.542 --> 33:24.753
<i>I found a couple new blisters</i>
<i>on my fingers,</i>

33:24.753 --> 33:26.922
but all in all,
I feel pretty good,

33:26.922 --> 33:29.674
<i>and I'm hoping that</i>
<i>we have a good day.</i>

33:29.674 --> 33:32.302
<i>I got 12 stitches sharpening</i>
<i>a knife once.</i>

33:32.302 --> 33:34.554
<i>That was fun.</i>

33:34.554 --> 33:36.890
<i>I decided not to test the</i>
<i>weapon after I completed it.</i>

