33:50.737 --> 33:52.697
You've had five days
at your home forges to work

33:52.697 --> 33:55.283
on your finale weapons.
Mark, how did it go?

33:55.283 --> 33:57.535
- It went pretty well, I think.

33:57.535 --> 34:01.331
<i>I used 51/60 for the blade,</i>
<i>bronze for the handle,</i>

34:01.331 --> 34:03.750
<i>hand-filed all the saw teeth</i>
<i>on the back.</i>

34:03.750 --> 34:07.087
I had a few ups and downs,
