34:07.087 --> 34:10.590
- All right. Nicholas, tell the
judges about your weapon.

34:10.590 --> 34:13.802
- Yeah, well,
I had some issues at first.

34:13.802 --> 34:17.389
<i>I went to do some 10/84 59/20</i>
<i>Damascus.</i>

34:17.389 --> 34:19.516
<i>Got into a few little things</i>
<i>I wasn't happy with,</i>

34:19.516 --> 34:22.560
<i>the worst of which is that</i>
<i>on day 5 I managed to snap it</i>

